text: FX is an Spanish pay television channel owned by Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA. The channel originally launched as the Spanish version of Discovery Health Channel on 6 November 2001. The channel was relaunched as Discovery Home & Health on 1 May 2005. On 11 May 2024, Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA announced that the Spanish version of Discovery Home & Health would be rebranded as FX on 16 August 2024. == Logos == file:Discovery H&H.png;|10 September 2011-16 August 2024 file:FX Logo 2023.svg|16 August 2024-present Category:Television channels in Europe
